erform in comparison to\nsimpler baselines. The code for the benchmark, its baselines, and a simple API\nfor evaluating new BDL tools are made available at\nhttps://github.com/oatml/bdl-benchmarks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Dec 2019 17:17:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-24"}
