cceleration technique based on a relaxation of the transmission\nconditions between the two subproblems. Numerical examples for linear and\nnonlinear problems are presented to validate the proposed methodology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Dec 2019 20:40:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Mar 2021 09:11:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-15"}
