2.5, representing\ndisequilibrium). Available data do not provide adequate constraints on maximum\nand minimum particle sizes for these power laws, so the model treats them as\nuser-selectable parameters for the simulant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Dec 2019 04:57:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Dec 2019 23:18:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-05"}
