d 15-20% of the gas forms a circumnuclear gas inside\n100 pc. This remnant gas heavily obscures the luminous phase of the active\ngalactic nuclei (AGN) during merger events, and the moderate AGN feedback does\nnot alter this property.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Dec 2019 05:16:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-26"}
