n. A variational inference\napproach is derived to train the proposed generative model. Thanks to the novel\ninference procedure and the robust initialization, the proposed MIN-VAE\nexhibits superior performance on speech enhancement than using the standard\naudio-only as well as audio-visual counterparts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Dec 2019 06:55:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 14:24:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 7 Jun 2020 17:19:42 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 8 Mar 2021 20:22:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-10"}
